---
import BlogPostLayout from '../../layouts/BlogPostLayout.astro';
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardDescription, CardContent } from '../../components/ui/card';
import { Button } from '../../components/ui/button';
import { Badge } from '../../components/ui/badge';
import { getBlogPost } from '../../lib/blog-posts';

// Export frontmatter for auto-discovery
export const frontmatter = {
  title: 'From Zero to Series A: Our Fundraising Journey',
  description: 'Lessons learned raising $5M in 6 months',
  author: 'David Kim',
  date: '2025-01-20',
  topic: 'entrepreneurship' as const,
  tags: ['fundraising', 'startups', 'vc', 'pitch deck', 'series-a'],
};

const post = getBlogPost('series-a-fundraising')!;
---

<BlogPostLayout post={post}>
  <p class="text-lg">
    Raising your Series A is a critical milestone that can make or break your startup's trajectory. After navigating the complexities of seed funding and proving product-market fit, the Series A represents your company's transition from experimentation to scaling. Here's what you need to know to close your round successfully.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 border-l-4 border-green-500 rounded-r-lg p-6 my-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">The Series A Landscape in 2025</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          Average Series A round size: <strong class="text-foreground">$15-20M</strong> •
          Median valuation: <strong class="text-foreground">$50-80M</strong> •
          Time to close: <strong class="text-foreground">3-6 months</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What Investors Look For</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <Card client:load className="border-l-4 border-l-primary">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Traction & Growth Metrics</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Proof that your business model works</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Revenue:</strong> $1M+ ARR (SaaS) or strong revenue trajectory</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Growth Rate:</strong> 15-20% month-over-month for at least 6 months</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>User Engagement:</strong> High retention and decreasing CAC</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Product-Market Fit:</strong> Clear evidence customers love your product</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load className="border-l-4 border-l-purple-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Team & Execution</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>The people who will execute the vision</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Domain Expertise:</strong> Founders who deeply understand the problem</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Track Record:</strong> Past successes or learnings from failures</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Key Hires:</strong> Senior talent in critical roles (CTO, Head of Sales)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Execution Velocity:</strong> Ability to ship fast and learn quickly</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load className="border-l-4 border-l-blue-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Market Opportunity</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>The size of the prize matters</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>TAM:</strong> Total addressable market of $1B+ (ideally $10B+)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Market Timing:</strong> Why now? What's changed recently?</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Competitive Moat:</strong> Defensible advantages and network effects</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Exit Potential:</strong> Clear path to acquisition or IPO</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>

    <Card client:load className="border-l-4 border-l-orange-500">
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle className="text-xl">Unit Economics & Financials</CardTitle>
        <CardDescription>Numbers that make sense</CardDescription>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>LTV:CAC Ratio:</strong> At least 3:1, ideally 5:1 or better</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Gross Margins:</strong> 70%+ for SaaS, 40%+ for marketplace</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Burn Multiple:</strong> Less than 1.5x (ideally under 1x)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Runway:</strong> 18-24 months post-raise to hit next milestones</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">The Fundraising Timeline</h2>

  <div class="relative my-8">
    <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-border"></div>

    <div class="relative pl-20 pb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary border-4 border-background"></div>
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <Badge client:load>Month 1-2</Badge>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Preparation</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">Polish your metrics, narrative, and deck. Build your target investor list. Get warm introductions.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold">Key deliverable: Compelling pitch deck + financial model</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative pl-20 pb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary border-4 border-background"></div>
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <Badge client:load>Month 2-3</Badge>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Initial Meetings</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">Start with 15-20 partner meetings. Refine your pitch based on feedback. Create FOMO by running a tight process.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold">Goal: 3-5 partners expressing strong interest</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative pl-20 pb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary border-4 border-background"></div>
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <Badge client:load>Month 3-4</Badge>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Deep Diligence</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">Customer calls, product demos, financial deep dives. Partner meetings with full investment committee.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold">Milestone: First term sheet received</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative pl-20 pb-8">
      <div class="absolute left-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary border-4 border-background"></div>
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <Badge client:load>Month 4-5</Badge>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Term Sheet Negotiation</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">Negotiate valuation, board seats, pro-rata rights, and other terms. Ideally have 2-3 competing offers.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold">Output: Signed term sheet with lead investor</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative pl-20">
      <div class="absolute left-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500 border-4 border-background"></div>
      <div class="bg-card border rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <Badge client:load variant="secondary">Month 5-6</Badge>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Legal & Close</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">Legal due diligence, document negotiation, final signatures. Fill out the round with strategic angels.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-green-600 font-semibold">Result: Money in the bank 🎉</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-amber-500/10 border-l-4 border-amber-500 rounded-r-lg p-6 my-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Common Pitfalls to Avoid</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <li>• Raising too early before proving product-market fit</li>
          <li>• Optimizing for valuation over finding the right partner</li>
          <li>• Failing to create competition and urgency among investors</li>
          <li>• Not leaving enough equity for future rounds and team incentives</li>
          <li>• Accepting unfavorable terms without proper legal review</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Building Your Pitch Deck</h2>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Your Series A deck should tell a compelling story in 15-20 slides. Here's the winning structure:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">01</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Problem</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">The painful problem you're solving</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">02</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Solution</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Your unique approach and product demo</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">03</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Market Size</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">TAM, SAM, SOM with bottoms-up analysis</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">04</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Traction</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Growth metrics that prove momentum</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">05</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Business Model</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">How you make money and unit economics</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">06</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Competition</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Landscape and your unfair advantages</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">07</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">Team</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Why you're uniquely qualified to win</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-muted rounded-lg p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
      <span class="font-bold text-primary flex-shrink-0">08</span>
      <div>
        <strong class="block mb-1">The Ask</strong>
        <span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Fundraise amount and use of funds</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Final Thoughts</h2>

  <p class="text-lg mb-6">
    Raising a Series A is a defining moment for your startup. It's not just about the money—it's about finding partners who believe in your vision and can help you navigate the challenges ahead. Choose wisely, negotiate fairly, and remember: the best time to raise is when you don't desperately need it.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
    <Button client:load variant="default">Download Pitch Deck Template</Button>
    <Button client:load variant="outline">View Financial Model</Button>
    <Button client:load variant="secondary">Book Strategy Call</Button>
  </div>

</BlogPostLayout>
